     * \return the moduli associated with the Truesdell' rate of the
     * Cauchy stress.
     * \param[in] Ks: tangent moduli in the logarithmic space
     * \param[in]  T: dual of the logarithmic strain
     */
    TFEL_HOST_DEVICE TangentOperator
